34:11.350 --> 34:13.216
Not that I remember.

34:13.719 --> 34:15.252
Well, you do.

34:15.254 --> 34:18.288
They're big and they're kind.

34:20.392 --> 34:23.693
The-- the cop who came told me
I-- I didn't have raisin eyes.

34:23.695 --> 34:25.796
What are raisin eyes?

34:27.466 --> 34:29.399
Fucking idiot.
Raisin eyes?

34:29.401 --> 34:30.801
[scoffs]
I know.

34:33.739 --> 34:37.174
If you have any questions
just call me.

34:40.612 --> 34:41.678
Thanks.

34:41.680 --> 34:45.415
[birds squawking]

34:56.095 --> 34:57.360
-[wood cracking]
-[gasps]

34:59.631 --> 35:00.797
Hello?

