39:54.659 --> 39:56.526
[birds chirping]

40:14.679 --> 40:16.112
[metal banging]

40:23.088 --> 40:24.521
Who's there?

40:26.124 --> 40:27.624
Is someone there?

40:28.093 --> 40:29.826
[wind howls]

40:31.430 --> 40:32.629
